DataList.LocalizeJP: 見る目あるじゃない。
DataList.LocalizeEN: You have a discerning eye, don't you?

DataList.LocalizeJP: その依頼受けてあげるわ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I will accept that request.

DataList.LocalizeJP: この着物、高いんだから！扱いには気をつけなさいよ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Come on! This kimono is expensive. Handle it carefully!

DataList.LocalizeJP: この服、高かったのに。
DataList.LocalizeEN: How could this happen? This outfit was expensive.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 今日はこんなところで勘弁してあげるわ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: That's enough. I'll let you off this time.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 私のようなリーダーにふさわしい仕事ね。
DataList.LocalizeEN: It's a good job for a leader like me.

DataList.LocalizeJP: その信頼に応えてあげるわ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I will live up to that trust.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 当然の結果ね。
DataList.LocalizeEN: What else did you expect?

DataList.LocalizeJP: どう？これが格の違いってやつよ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: How's that? This is what being outmatched is like.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 助かるわ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Thank you.

DataList.LocalizeJP: さあ、行くわよ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Come on, let's go.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 安全を確保したわ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I secured a safe spot.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 何なのよ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: What's your problem!

DataList.LocalizeJP: ここで引いてたまるもんですか！
DataList.LocalizeEN: I'm not about to retreat now!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 無駄よ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: It's useless.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 勇猛精進。さあ、始めるわよ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: "Yuumou shoujin". Let's get started.

DataList.LocalizeJP: さあ、今年も仕事始めと行きましょうか。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Let's get to work again this year, yes?

DataList.LocalizeJP: ほら！グズグズしてる時間はないわよ
DataList.LocalizeEN: Hey! There's no time to linger.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 次行くわよ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Here goes the next one.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 感謝するわ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Thank you.

DataList.LocalizeJP: こんなのおみくじに書いてなかったのに。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I didn't write this on my fortune slip.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 移動するわ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Changing position.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 今年の運勢は見るまでもなく大吉みたいね。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Looks like this year I got Great Fortune. No need to look at a fortune slip.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 今年も立ち上がりから完璧ね。
DataList.LocalizeEN: This year, too, perfect right from the start.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 見てなさい、私の実力。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Look at my true strength.

DataList.LocalizeJP: しっかりと見てなさい。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Look closely.

DataList.LocalizeJP: これぐらい朝飯前。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Piece of cake.

DataList.LocalizeJP: うぁ、ちょっ！チェスト！
さすがは私。まだまだ成長の余地があるということね。
DataList.LocalizeEN: As expected of me, there is still room for growth.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 私の進化がますます発揮されつつあるわね。
DataList.LocalizeEN: My progress is showing more and more.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 私のすごさようやくわかったかしら。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Did you you finally understand how amazing I am?

DataList.LocalizeJP: こうしてどんどん強くなる私のことをもっともっと頼ってもいいのよ、先生。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Sensei, you can rely more and more on me now that I'm growing stronger.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 先生と私なかなかいいパートナーだと思わない？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Me and Sensei, we make for great partners, don't you think?

DataList.LocalizeJP: 喜びなさい。これからもずっと一緒にいてあげるわ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Rejoice, I will always stay by your side.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 先生は私にとってもう単なる依頼人じゃなくて…そ、その…そう！VIPなのよ！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Sensei is no longer just a client for me... because, well... because you're VIP now!

DataList.LocalizeJP: いつの間にか先生とこんなところまで来ていたなんて。今年はもちろん、来年もよろしく頼むわね、先生。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Before I knew it, I had come all the way here with Sensei. Please look after me this year, and the next year too.
